reviewText: I Expedited something totally different from these guys. that its the goodwill but I was wrong so wrong the Movie I Order was listed as NEW and I thought with it being the Goodwill it would be mangled and torn up and it wasn't. everything was exactly what they said it would be Perfect. way to good you surprised me....
I got it pretty fast and I loved it. There was no damage, great condition. Two great movies together at a great price.
I loved the movie came in great shape, Just what I wanted, Great to watch with my kids and husband

I enjoyed the Wedding Planner and decided to take a chance on the double DVD since I hadn't seen the other movie before. Big mistake. My Best Friends Wedding just made me so mad at her horrible behavior! I could not find any reason to defend her actions. You can be jealous that your love is getting married, but don't be such a cold-hearted saboteur when he doesn't return the affection. You've been friend-zoned, get over it home-wrecker. If you have seen this movie before and liked it then go ahead and buy these two. But otherwise I recommend getting the Wedding Planner on its own!
I love these romantic comedy movies and a double feature is a bonus.  The price is a great deal also.
the dvd wasn't scratched, was in perfect condition/good as new, was shipped to me on time (in fact a day early I believe), and love these movies! old classics! I recommend buying these movies.
this movie is worth everypenny and of course you cant forget Julia roberts over all its a great movie
both are great movies. very romantic.
Thanks so much.

If you are feeling bored, these are the movies you want to see. They will make you laugh. And a cup of wine.
I am a movie lover. So this is a great opportunity to obtain two of my favorite movies. And for the price WOW!!!
These two movies are both winners, funny, spicy, well acted and well supported.  Enjoyed them both and recommend with no hesitations.
